     "License" means this document.
     "Program" means the source code, object code, and associated files
     distributed under this License.
     "You" means an individual or legal entity using the Program.
     "Derivative Work" means any modification of the Program or work
     based on the Program.
     "Qualifying Entity" means a commercial entity (or group of
     affiliated entities) that meets at least one of the following
     criteria at any time during the term of use:
          a) 500 or more employees; or
          b) annual revenue exceeding 100 million USD.
     "Commercial Use" means any use of the Program that is intended
     for or results in commercial advantage or monetary compensation,
     including but not limited to:
          a) incorporating the Program into products or services sold
             to third parties;
          b) using the Program to provide paid services;
          c) selling copies of the Program;
          d) using the Program for internal business operations if the
             entity's primary business is commercial and more than 50%
             of its revenue derives from commercial activities.
     "Licensor" means the original copyright holder(s) of the Program.

